_sText:
Created for Bental for use on his WCS server.
Special thanks to [frank.] for mapping support.

40 spawn points per team (making it suitable for up to 80-slot servers,) buy zones, weapons with full ammo laid out at spawns, fall damage disabled, basic 3D skybox, topped off with a lovely visual style. No custom content used, all stock textures. Third map I've released, first on Gamebanana, first non-jailbreak release.

Feel free to use it on your servers.
